2 BMO Asset Management Inc. was awarded Best ETF Initiative at the 19th annual Morningstar Canadian Investment Awards. BMO Asset Management was acknowledged for promoting education and awareness in the Exchange Traded Fund (ETF) industry; and building relationships with the investing and advisor communities.































