BMO Global Asset Management Canada, Institutional







We work closely with our clients to identify and understand their needs and challenges. We leverage the skills of our global platform to identify the best solution.
  
Introducing Our Services & Solutions
 
BMO GAM is a global platform with one vision, to offer innovative, outcome-oriented investment solutions that deliver on clients’ needs.
 
Learn more







Who we help
How we help




We focus on meeting the unique requirements of Canadian institutional clients. They include pension funds, endowments, trusts, First Nations, insurance companies and corporate assets.


Our mission is to demonstrate innovation in action by distinguishing ourselves in our approach to research/portfolio construction, the calibre of investment solutions we offer, and the quality of client service we provide.




We offer an unwavering commitment to excellence, integrity and service quality. We draw upon the skills and expertise of our teams from around the world, and offer solutions that range from full replication to high-conviction strategies, span geographies and asset classes, encompass various investment approaches, and address varying risk profiles.



Assets under management in excess of C$313 billion*
25 offices in 14 countries across 5 continents to serve clients
Strong investment performance







